    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "session_flow_legend_body",
      "x": 1012, "y": 596,
      "width": 576, "height": 450,
      "text": "WS Connect:\n  1. Frontend opens WS /ws/{session_id}?token=JWT\n  2. JWT Middleware validates → user_id extracted\n  3. SessionManager creates/resumes session in SQLite\n  4. DuckDB context reloaded (eager) if session resumed\n\nQuery Execution:\n  5. Client sends { type:\"query\", prompt }\n  6. WSManager dispatches to LangChain AgentExecutor\n  7. Agent ← Anthropic API (claude-sonnet-4-6)\n  8. Agent calls get_schema() → GetSchema RPC\n  9. Agent generates SQL → run_sql() → RunSQL RPC\n  10. DuckDB svc executes → returns rows + CSV path\n  11. File saved to results/{query_id}/step_N.csv\n  12. WSManager streams ← partial_result per step\n  13. Final result → final_result message\n  14. queries + steps rows written to SQLite\n\nDisconnect/Reconnect:\n  15. WS close → session stays alive (TTL 30 min)\n  16. Reconnect → resume same session_id\n  17. APScheduler (every 5 min) → expire old sessions\n\nDownload:\n  18. GET /files/download/{query_id} + JWT\n  19. FastAPI generates signed URL (low TTL)\n  20. Frontend redirects → download CSV",
      "originalText": "WS Connect:\n  1. Frontend opens WS /ws/{session_id}?token=JWT\n  2. JWT Middleware validates → user_id extracted\n  3. SessionManager creates/resumes session in SQLite\n  4. DuckDB context reloaded (eager) if session resumed\n\nQuery Execution:\n  5. Client sends { type:\"query\", prompt }\n  6. WSManager dispatches to LangChain AgentExecutor\n  7. Agent ← Anthropic API (claude-sonnet-4-6)\n  8. Agent calls get_schema() → GetSchema RPC\n  9. Agent generates SQL → run_sql() → RunSQL RPC\n  10. DuckDB svc executes → returns rows + CSV path\n  11. File saved to results/{query_id}/step_N.csv\n  12. WSManager streams ← partial_result per step\n  13. Final result → final_result message\n  14. queries + steps rows written to SQLite\n\nDisconnect/Reconnect:\n  15. WS close → session stays alive (TTL 30 min)\n  16. Reconnect → resume same session_id\n  17. APScheduler (every 5 min) → expire old sessions\n\nDownload:\n  18. GET /files/download/{query_id} + JWT\n  19. FastAPI generates signed URL (low TTL)\n  20. Frontend redirects → download CSV",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 500017,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 500018,
      "isDeleted": false,
